<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><lyrics>[V1]
 wǒ men shì shén suǒ zào ō. wǒ men dōu yǒu shén de róng yào ō.
 xīn lǐ yuè sī xiǎng jiù yuè zhī dào, tā de míng zì jiù shì jiào qí miào.
 jiù rén huàn chéng xīn rén, zhēn qí miào. xìn kào tā yǒng yuǎn bù huì lǎo, zhēn qí miào.
 qí miào de shì ruò yī yī shù suàn, quán shì jiè dōu róng bù le.
 qí miào ya zhēn qí miào. fēng chuī shù yè ér yáo.
 qí miào ya zhēn qí miào. xìn de rén cái néng tǐ huì dào.</lyrics>
<title>yé sū zhēn qí miào 迦南727</title>
<hymn_number>727</hymn_number>
<author>lǚ xiǎo mǐn</author>
</song>